  <metadesc>PET index - PET emulators</metadesc>
  <overview><p>
	PET computers are increasingly hard to get. So, on one side, there are emulators
	that allow to run PET programs on other hardware. 
	</p><p>
	Also, in the recent couple of years (relative to 2026 where I write this), some new hardware rebuilds, and even
	mixups with a new hardware just running a PET emulator have come up.
	</p><p>
	This page tries to describe the different emulators available.
	</p>
  </overview>
